Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:09.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We need to become the MVPs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We're stopping the Quest \NDorm from getting shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:13.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,and Souta from getting expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane/Kikuno/Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:28.34,Kanojo_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}If {\c&H53AC43&}Her {\c&H085DF0&}Flag {\c&HD2C345&}Breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:52.00,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Number,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(734,1)\c&HE792AA&}Flag {\c&H3CDC9A&}4
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:52.00,Kanojo_Flag_Ep_Title,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(734,1)}We're {\c&HA24FD8&}Almost to the {\c&H38AEE2&}Goal. {\c&HA24FD8&}The Track Meet{\c&H65B895&}'ll End {\c&HDACA50&}Just Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So this might be a bit late,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:58.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but what do we need \Nto do to become MVPs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:00.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,we need to get a high total score,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,but the score's not the only thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:08.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of emphasis \Nplaced on special points
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,you can get for teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, whoever stands \Nout the most, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've chosen which games you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,should be able to get the most points in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:18.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing all these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.12,Sports_Week_02:20,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Sports Week
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.12,Daytime_02:20,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Daytime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.12,Mon_02:20,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.12,Tue_02:20,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Tuesday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:23.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,This does go on for a whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,A proper schedule is the key to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's time for me to go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I have the 100 meter preliminaries right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,The women's preliminaries \Nare still a while off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.97,Ta-da_02:37,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:42.60,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for our special Sports Week \Nprogram, {\i0}If I Don't do It, Who Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.17,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your host, Seiteikouji Mimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:48.56,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,My guest here is Hatagaya Academy's own \Nwalking dictionary, Ryuukishibara Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.31,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.22,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young, \NI was the anchor for a bucket relay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.77,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,when the town was on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:58.17,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Our program will pick up \Nany news-worthy events
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:01.03,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,that happen around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.91,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,First we had Hatagaya Academy's \Nfirst martial arts tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:07.59,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Surrounded by tough competitors, \Nonly one could stand on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:10.03,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,And Eiyuuzaki Rin-kun was that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:12.54,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure you'd see that at a track meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.67,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Next we had the heavyweight \Ncat-gathering competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.00,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,The android everyone's talking \Nabout, Ninjabayashi Ruri-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:24.11,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,used the speaker in her mouth to broadcast \Na sound which only cats could hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.45,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,and gathered them all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.26,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what this \Nis supposed to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.52,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,And we had a teacher massage contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.90,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,This was just a throw-in for the teachers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.31,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,It's still the first day and \Nwe've hit the ground running!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.56,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,The Quest Dorm team is \Nreally tearing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:41.15,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone cheer the Quest Dorm on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she feels responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you did a good job, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You got first in the princess race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.03,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Only real princesses can participate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.01,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why would there be an event like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:04.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ref,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ref,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start our \Npenalty shoot-out competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's a penalty shoot-out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:14.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,It's where you do soccer \Npenalty kicks over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,It's a contest that measures one's \Nstate of mind and composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Can Souta really handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can do it, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.16,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This worked well for Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You were great, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're moving on to the finals, Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Good work, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:54.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're able to read people \Nbetter than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll win tomorrow's \Nfinals just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta/Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Megu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You just called for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Megu! They must have screwed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,because they just announced \Nyou set a new course record!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I did just get a new record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:13.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You guys didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,She was constantly a contender in the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,middle school championships \Nfor track-and-field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Megu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were \Nin track-and-field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not in track-and-field anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you in, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,The home ec club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Totally should have expected that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Gallop, gallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you on a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:42.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I was just in a horse-riding \Ncompetition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you still riding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I just kind of felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What's your next event?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:56.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:58.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,For safety's sake, hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:18.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,White King, hiyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You all did great out there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently in first place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,However, we still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:31.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Those that have night events \Nwill sleep after eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I will not have anyone oversleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Night events... Early morning events...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:38.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That student council president \Nnever does anything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But this is kinda fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda feels like we're \Non a club trip somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:47.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's always felt like we were \Nall on a trip together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say we're having a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:51.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,"strengthen our friendships" camp right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Your poems are always so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stop saying poem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I take that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:07:00.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,We've all become one to help you, Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,We really are strengthening our bonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:05.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're putting our friendships \Non the line to get that MVP spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:09.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really a friend, \Nbut an older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not really becoming closer \Nfriends, but loving him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,All of you can love him more, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I think you get along with him best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:25.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What? I-I think that \NMegu-chan is best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it can't be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think Rin-senpai is best. \NShe's known him since they were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.55,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,They're all trying to \Nhand him to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We've decided to leave the love part to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan, through process of elimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're just pushing it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let this go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:10.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Living like this is spoiling me, \Nand it's causing me to forget everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.72,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the shoot out finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.98,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,If he stops this shot, \Nthe Quest Dorm team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, we're here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! \NStop it with sheer willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.16,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.86,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,The handicraft team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently in eighth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,The last day is tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think we'd have such a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,The men's teams are coming after us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,like they're getting revenge \Nfor their little brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:21.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to save Souta-kun's Quest Dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I am a machine whose \Npurpose is to help humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri, what are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-san and the others are \Nexperiencing a dip in their morale vectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I have inferred that this is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,strongly connected to the current decline
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,in your morale vector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,It is fatal if someone's morale vector\Ndrops below a certain point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:58.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,My "pursuit of human happiness" program
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,suggests that this issue be resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The reason everything is \Nlike this will be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:09.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Is that because you've \Nresolved yourself to defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri, let's talk where no one else is around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,going to die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot comprehend the concept of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:40.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware that humans instinctively
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,fear death, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of dying, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but there's something \NI'm even more afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,When I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,everyone else may feel \Nsorrow because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make those that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,care about me feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm most afraid of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave the school on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,then the wounds I inflict \Nwill be much less deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to clean things up after I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:11.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no way to avoid your death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:11.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:17.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I understood how to destroy other people's \Ndeath flags in an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but my own flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. That letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Princess knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:26.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,bishop, ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,First Flag secret code: entry confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,White hacking mode released.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting directly to server.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Direct access to kernel space granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ruri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you wish to proceed \Nto the "shadows" of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish to make any corrections?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The "shadows" of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:58.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,The first gate that will be \Nopened by the four heroes that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,fly the Royal Banner is connected to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,the "shadows" of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,There waits one will destroy the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:08.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,flag of death that eats \Naway at the Royal Banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:11.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The flag of death? Will destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean I can get \Nrid of this death flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But... who...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:25.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of a girl named Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I do contain some data \Nof a word close that one,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,however I am unable to \Nlearn more at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you know where \Nthis "first gate" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:41.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for a readable cluster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:43.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to project the program?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:46.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Quest Dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Royal Banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:06.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane, and Ruri, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:13.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So this person is the bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:40.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,This is most likely the first gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:50.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakara,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakara,0000,0000,0000,,And in exchange, you must
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sakara,0000,0000,0000,,learn the ultimate truth of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:03.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Last updated: 1938.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,The record was created \Nby Ninjabayashi Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri, you've been around that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,No, I began test operations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:16.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I must assume it was \Nsomeone by the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then was there anyone \Nat Hatagaya Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,with a word meaning \N"bishop" in their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:24.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Searching database.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Zero results.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:31.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know where this data came \Nfrom, or even if it can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,if that door really does exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can't leave Quest Dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate truth of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If I can reach it, then I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The others might not have to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,You need... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:01.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,There have been plenty of \Npeople who tolerated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,But for someone to say they needed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:07.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta-san, you're the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.94,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last day for Sports Week!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.94,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,The last event is an obstacle \Nrelay race around the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.21,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,If you manage to use your teamwork to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.99,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,get around the various obstacles \Nlaid out in this large course,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.20,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,you might be able to get MVP \Nfrom an underdog position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So if we win, we're MVPs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That makes things easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this'll work...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The final runners have to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:43.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,run in pairs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The victory flags've been raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ref,0000,0000,0000,,On your marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ref,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.55,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.03,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.28,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.60,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Please win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:05.79,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that I wouldn't try?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:06.76,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:09.08,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.14,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then could I ask something of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.61,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:15.62,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.66,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Kikuno-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:22.62,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.09,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making \Nyou worry all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:25.92,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and being such a terrible \Nlittle brother character,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.00,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but I want you to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a little brother character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.60,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.78,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:38.35,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Older sisters are invincible when \Nit comes to their little brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Megu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.46,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.31,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.83,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.11,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I understand... I understand, Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.61,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Pop, pop, pop, pop, pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.61,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Men don't need words to promise \Nsomething to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:58.91,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-kun, thank you for \Ntrying so hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.66,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.46,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,N-No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.97,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been best friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:07.96,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:12.00,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You could never be replaced in my heart—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.34,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,you were my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.73,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.49,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Pop, pop, pop, pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.91,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to show me how \Ncool you can be, once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.14,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:29.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you were \Nrunning around all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was just using everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,They fall head over heels for you, \Nand you're worried about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I don't really \Ncare about this MVP stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't like losing to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to get your victory \Nflag up, even though I knew the others—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:54.84,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've never seen a flag of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.84,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Does Nanami not have flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stay in the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're going to be MVPs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Show us what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.01,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,Quest Dorm team is in first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:27.68,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,All they have to do is put \Ntheir ice on the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.97,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,and run to the goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Just a small scrape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:45.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's only half a lap left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:50.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we the anchors if we can't deliver the sash,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,containing everyone's feelings, \Nto the finish line properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Let's go, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's the last spurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, you saved me from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a victory flag, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:16.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:18.88,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Will I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:22.14,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,only bring sorrow to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.82,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is it right for me to just disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:28.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.32,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But I still want to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.07,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,...with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.93,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,...there at Quest Dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.33,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,Quest Dorm team is catching \Nup at a crazy pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:58.30,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,Who got to the finish line first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.80,Teams_19:58,A,0000,0000,0000,,Quest Dorm Team \N\N\NBaseball Team
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.80,relay_19:58,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hatagaya Academy \NAround the school obstacle relay
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:05.39,Photo_Finish_19:58,A,0000,0000,0000,,Photo finish
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.25,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Photo finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:01.72,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,First is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:05.39,1st_20:01,A,0000,0000,0000,,1st Place: Baseball Team
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:05.39,2nd_20:01,A,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Place: Quest Dorm Team
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:05.39,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,First is the baseball team!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.14,Kanojo_Flag_Announcer,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Quest Dorm team is a close second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:12.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So what does this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Souta-kun is going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:16.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:19.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:24.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad I got to work so hard \Ntowards something with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at fault here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't been hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We were moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:39.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,These are the people on the board \Nthat were complaining about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:43.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You had an accident, and you still \Ncarried your friend to the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You believed in your friends \Nto the last minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:47.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,and called out to them, cheering them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:51.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,This is true friendship, true teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:54.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't change the fact that \NSouta will be kicked out of the dorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Second place and better are pretty \Nmuch guaranteed to get MVP.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:58.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Quest Dorm gets to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:11.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami/Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he's the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:14.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The athletic festival's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:16.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what everyone thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.94,0:23:18.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't set up a continuation flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:20.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring Mimori's nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:23.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,what are you planning to do for break \Nnow that the festival's over, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:26.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've been busy lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:27.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,so I've been thinking \Nof relaxing at the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:30.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what everyone thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:32.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep setting up these flags!
