Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:34.93,Kanojo_Flag_Next_Ep_Title,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Believe {\c&HDAB776&}and Wait for Me. \N{\c&H9650D9&}I'm not {\c&H3DB6E7&}Going to be Late{\c&H5DBC91&} for My Date {\c&HD1C35E&}With Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:33.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
